&lt;p&gt;As a &lt;strong&gt;Director of Implementation&lt;/strong&gt;, you will lead the strategic direction of implementation and customer onboarding across a portfolio of enterprise customers. You will oversee implementation teams, guide architectural design of customer solutions, and collaborate closely with Product, Engineering, and Revenue teams to ensure the platform evolves in alignment with customer needs and business priorities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you’re passionate about &lt;strong&gt;building high-performing teams, driving customer impact through data and technology, and shaping the future of sales operations&lt;/strong&gt;, we’d love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
