&lt;li&gt;Build, mentor, and lead a &lt;strong&gt;high-performing implementation team&lt;/strong&gt;, establishing best practices, processes, and standards for delivery excellence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with executive leadership to align &lt;strong&gt;customer implementation strategy with company growth and product roadmap priorities&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish &lt;strong&gt;KPIs and success metrics&lt;/strong&gt; for implementation performance, customer outcomes, and operational efficiency.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
